      "content": "that's intense, definitely got the vibe. i want to add more detail about the people living there to really sell the sense of danger. can you describe some of the groups or types of people hanging out on the corners or in the alleys? i want to capture the specific look and feel of the people who make this place feel so sketchy and unpredictable.",
